data.name: grdXRT.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.XRAY_CODE , A.XRAY_NAME , A.XRAY_GUBUN , A.XRAY_ROOM , A.XRAY_BUWI , A.XRAY_BUWI_KAIKEI , A.XRAY_BUWI_TONG , A.XRAY_CNT , A.NAME_PRINT_YN , A.SUGA_CODE , A.SPECIAL_YN , A.XRAY_REAL_CNT , A.SLIP_CODE , A.RESER_TYPE , B.CODE_NAME GUBUN_NAME , G.CODE_NAME ROOM_NAME , C.BUWI_NAME BUWI_NAME , I.BUWI_NAME BUWI_KAIKEI_NAME , D.BUWI_NAME BUWI_TONG_NAME , H.CODE_NAME RESER_TYPE_NAME , A.JAERYO_YN , A.SORT , A.XRAY_WAY , A.FREQUENT_USE_YN , A.MODALITY , J.CODE_NAME MODALITY_NAME , LPAD(A.SORT,4,'0') , A.XRAY_NAME2 , A.TONG_GUBUN , A.REQUEST_YN FROM XRT0102 J , XRT0122 I , XRT0102 H , XRT0102 G , XRT0102 F , XRT0102 E , XRT0122 D , XRT0122 C , XRT0102 B , XRT0001 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND F.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND G.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND H.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND I.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND J.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.XRAY_GUBUN <> 'R' AND B.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'X1' AND A.XRAY_GUBUN = B.CODE(+) AND C.BUWI_CODE(+) = A.XRAY_BUWI AND I.BUWI_CODE(+) = A.XRAY_BUWI_KAIKEI AND D.BUWI_CODE(+) = A.XRAY_BUWI_TONG AND E.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'X4' AND A.XRAY_WAY = E.CODE(+) AND F.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'X5' AND A.XRAY_RIGHT = F.CODE(+) AND G.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'X6' AND A.XRAY_ROOM = G.CODE(+) AND H.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'Y' AND H.CODE(+) = A.RESER_TYPE AND J.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'MO' AND A.MODALITY = J.CODE(+) AND (NVL(A.XRAY_CODE,'%') LIKE '%'||nvl(:f_txtParam,'%') ||'%' OR NVL(A.XRAY_NAME,'%') LIKE '%'||nvl(:f_txtParam,'%') ||'%') AND NVL(A.XRAY_GUBUN,'%') LIKE '%'||nvl(:f_xray_gubun,'%') ||'%' AND NVL(A.SPECIAL_YN,'%') LIKE '%'||nvl(:f_special_yn,'%') ||'%' ORDER BY A.XRAY_CODE

data.name: cbxXrayGubun.UserSQL
data.value: SELECT '' CODE , '' CODE_NAME FROM DUAL UNION SELECT CODE , CODE_NAME FROM XRT0102 WHERE HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND CODE_TYPE = 'X1' ORDER BY CODE NULLS FIRST

data.name: grdRadioList.QuerySQL
data.value: -- RADIO INFO-- SELECT A.XRAY_CODE , A.XRAY_GUBUN , A.XRAY_CODE_IDX , A.XRAY_CODE_IDX_NM , A.TUBE_VOL , A.TUBE_CUR , A.XRAY_TIME , A.TUBE_CUR_TIME , A.IRRADIATION_TIME , A.XRAY_DISTANCE FROM XRT0002 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.XRAY_CODE = :f_xray_code ORDER BY A.XRAY_GUBUN, A.XRAY_CODE, A.XRAY_CODE_IDX
